In Ubuntu, launch the native terminal and type the following command:
apt-get update

This will proceed to update all repos for apps and dependencies.
sudo apt-get install -y build-essential kernel-package libncurses5-dev bzip2

Now we need some toolchains i use my Script file where i mentiond toolchain repo check it on my git 

To install OpenSSL development package on Ubuntu or their derivatives:
sudo apt-get install libssl-dev
